high_descs: Turn around, walk towards the counter, and then turn left towards the toaster on the count.
Pick up the knife to the right of the toaster.
Turn around and head towards the sink on your left.
Slice the apple in the sink into three pieces.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn left and head towards the microwave above the oven.
Place the apple in the microwave, heat it up, and take it back out.
Take a step left to face the counter.
Place the apple to the left of the spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm slice of apple on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk over to the counter and turn left, then walk up to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the butter knife to the left of the toaster on the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Slice up the rightmost apple in the sink basin.
Place the butter knife in the sink to the right of the sliced apple.
Pick up an apple slice out of the sink basin.
Turn around and begin walking across the room, the hang a right and walk over to the oven and look up at the microwave.
Open the microwave door and put the apple slice in to the right of the egg, then microwave it for a couple seconds, after that remove the apple slice and close the microwave door.
Turn left and walk over to the end of the counter, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the heated apple slice on the edge of the counter to the left of the spoon o the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter, turn left, go forward to the counter with the toaster.
Take the knife on the right of the toaster.
Turn around, go forward then make a left towards the sink.
Cut the right apple in the sink into pieces.
Put the knife in the sink to the right of the cut apple.
Take a piece of apple from the sink.
Turn around, go forward, turn right and go forward to the oven.
Cook the apple in the microwave. Take the apple from the microwave.
Go to the counter to the left of the oven and face it.
Put the apple on the left of the spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on a counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife to the right of the toaster.
Turn and walk to the sink on the left.
Slice the red apple that's in the right side of the sink.
Put the knife down in the sink to the right of the sliced red apple.
Pick up a slice of the red apple closest to the butter knife.
Turn around and walk to the microwave above the stove.
Put the apple slice in the microwave to the right of the egg, heat up the apple slice, take the apple slice out of the microwave.
Walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Place the piece of apple to the left of the spoon on the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of apple and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and walk over to the toaster on the counter.
Pick up the metal knife that is on the counter to the right of the toaster.
Turn around and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Slice up the rightmost tomato that is in the sink basin.
Put the metal knife into the sink basin to the right of the sliced apple.
Pick up an apple slice out of the sink basin.
Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk over to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple slice in to the right of the egg then close the door and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take the apple slice out and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk over to the section of counter to the left of the stove.
Put the heated piece of sliced apple on the counter to the left of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple slice on the counter.
